<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <!-- Include head partial -->
    <%- include('./partials/head.ejs', { title: 'About Us - Blog Ninja' }) %>

    <style>
        /* Reset some default browser styles */
        body, h1, h2, h3, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Style for the overall body */
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            color: #333;
            padding-bottom: 60px; /* Ensure there's space for the footer */
        }

        /* Container for flex alignment */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Style for the main content area */
        .content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Style for the section titles */
        .title {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #34495e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1abc9c;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        /* Style for the paragraphs */
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin: 15px 0 25px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Image styling */
        .about-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Flexbox for the team section */
        .team {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .team-member {
            flex: 1 1 200px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .team-member img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include navigation bar -->
    <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="title">About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Blog Ninja, your number one source for all things blogging. We're dedicated to providing you the very best of blog posts, with an emphasis on quality content, insightful analysis, and engaging stories.</p>
            <p>Founded in 2023 by Jane Doe, Blog Ninja has come a long way from its beginnings in a home office. When Jane first started out, her passion for blogging drove her to start her own business.</p>
            <p>We hope you enjoy our blogs as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
            
            <h2 class="title">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to provide our readers with the best possible content, whether it's about technology, lifestyle, health, or any other topic that interests them. We strive to create a platform where readers can find reliable, insightful, and engaging content.</p>
            
            <h2 class="title">Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/100?random=1" alt="Jane Doe">
                    <h3>Jane Doe</h3>
                    <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/100?random=2" alt="John Smith">
                    <h3>John Smith</h3>
                    <p>Chief Content Officer</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/100?random=3" alt="Emily Davis">
                    <h3>Emily Davis</h3>
                    <p>Marketing Director</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/100?random=4" alt="Michael Brown">
                    <h3>Michael Brown</h3>
                    <p>Lead Developer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
